WEBVTT

00:00.498 --> 00:03.134
And then we can talk
about completing the mission.

00:05.970 --> 00:08.239
Dr. Mann, listen to me.

00:08.439 --> 00:12.209
This is not about my life...
or Cooper's life.

00:12.343 --> 00:13.845
This is about all mankind.

00:13.978 --> 00:15.079
[beeping]

00:15.213 --> 00:17.715
There is a moment-
[thudding]

00:22.820 --> 00:24.122
It is not-

00:32.797 --> 00:33.865
Oh my God.

00:40.938 --> 00:42.874
[engine running]

00:51.649 --> 00:54.418
Cooper, there's no point
in using our fuel to chase-

00:54.552 --> 00:56.154
Just analyze
the Endurance's spin.

01:01.025 --> 01:02.060
What are you doing?

01:02.260 --> 01:03.595
Docking.

01:07.731 --> 01:10.435
Endurance rotation is 67,
68 rpm.

01:10.568 --> 01:11.969
Okay, get ready to match
our spin

01:12.103 --> 01:13.404
with the retro-thruster's.

01:13.537 --> 01:17.175
- It's not possible.
- No. It's necessary.

01:28.519 --> 01:30.421
Endurance is hitting
stratosphere.

01:35.059 --> 01:36.594
She's got no heat shield.

01:39.597 --> 01:41.766
- Case, you ready?
- Ready.

01:49.774 --> 01:52.844
Cooper, this is no time
for caution.

01:54.745 --> 01:56.948
Case, if I black out,
you take the stick.

01:57.382 --> 02:00.351
TARS, get ready to engage
the docking mechanism.
